<h2 class="mw-headline" id="Upgrading_the_CDF">Upgrading the CDF</h2>
<p>The 2019.11 CDF can upgrade from 2019.08. The upgrade will update all components such as Docker, Kubernetes, Heapster, Vault, Etcd, Flannel and the CDF core to the 2019.11 level.
</p><p>The upgrade process is done by executing an orchestrator auto-upgrade script or by manually executing the upgrade scripts on all of the cluster nodes.
</p><p>An upgrade should only occur when:
</p>
<ul><li>An upgrade of the installed 2019.05 or 2019.08 suite is imminent.</li>
<li>The installed 2019.05/2019.08-compatible Suite is uninstalled and a 2019.11 Suite will be installed next.</li></ul>
<p>For details on the CDF upgrade, see the Administration Guide.
</p>
